cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Speech and Audio Processing): The paper focuses on speech processing, specifically on the Silent Speech Challenge benchmark. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper discusses language models and decoding scenarios. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a Deep Learning strategy and auto-encoder-based features. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses neural networks in the Deep Learning strategy. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses machine learning and neural networks, which are subfields of AI.
